data.description: Welcome home to this adorable, 2-year, all-electric home bursting with high-quality builder updates, tuck away in the heart of Festus boasting vinyl siding, enclosed soffits/fascia, 30-yr architectural shingle roof, insulated tilt-in windows, impressive curb appeal, & cozy covered porch w/solar light. Enter into a sun-filled, open floorplan showcasing striking LVP floors, neutral paint, warm classic décor, & brush nickel light fixtures throughout. Stunning eat-in kitchen shares the spotlight with custom 42” white cabinets, granite-like countertops, ceramic tile backsplash, SS appliances, & convenient laundry area. 2 spacious bedrooms both w/deep closets & ceiling fans. Gorgeous bathroom featuring ceramic tile floors, vanity, & beautiful ceramic tile backsplash that extends wall-to-wall. Step outside to a large backyard perfect for entertaining & prime location for shopping, dining, & major hwys a perfect blend of both. Fantastic opportunity before the holidays. WOW!
